name: Meme Man
description: Meme Man Token is a memecoin based on the 3D-rendered head character from 2016 that popularized surreal meme formats including "Stonks," "Panik/Kalm," and "Helth." The cryptocurrency project draws inspiration from the character's significance in internet meme culture and its widespread use across social media platforms. The token operates as a decentralized digital asset celebrating this notable meme figure.
